div.p:
A man cometh into a wood,32. E. 3. fol. 32. and cutteth and taketh
away trees to the value of 20. s. it is not felony;
for they bee parcell of the Franktenement;
but otherwiſe it is if a man ſteale away trees that
bee felled.

The Wife taketh the goods of her Husband,13. E. 4. and
carryeth them away ſecretly, this is not felony;
Quaere the Receiver.
